  collabPresetCodeFixLeadTask:   {"zh-CN": "由 Hermes 负责阅读代码、定位问题、编写修复方案并输出补丁。", "zh-TW": "由 Hermes 負責閱讀程式碼、定位問題、編寫修復方案並輸出補丁。", "en": "Hermes reads the code, locates the issue, drafts the fix, and outputs the patch."},
  collabPresetCodeFixSupportTask:{"zh-CN": "由 OpenClaw 负责执行构建、测试、运行验证，并返回失败日志或通过结论。", "zh-TW": "由 OpenClaw 負責執行建置、測試、執行驗證，並返回失敗日誌或通過結論。", "en": "OpenClaw runs builds, tests, and runtime verification, then returns failure logs or a pass result."},
