  collabPresetDocPlanSupportTask:{"zh-CN": "由 OpenClaw 负责核对实现可行性、命令可执行性和环境差异。", "zh-TW": "由 OpenClaw 負責核對實作可行性、命令可執行性和環境差異。", "en": "OpenClaw checks implementation feasibility, command executability, and environment differences."},
